To build and scale effective use of AI tools is crucial for our long-term data strategy. You will help define and implement prompt engineering standards, making AI a productive collaborator across departments.

Understand internal stakeholders' needs related to AI and data usage, and translate them into effective prompt strategies.

Design, test, and optimize prompts for LLMs (e.g., ChatGPT, Gemini).

Develop reusable prompt chains and templates that standardize interactions with AI.

Monitor prompt performance and iterate based on output quality and user feedback.

Collaborate with data professionals to integrate LLMs into reporting, analysis, and automation pipelines.

Stay up to date on best practices and advancements in the prompt engineering space.

Promote ethical use and governance of generative AI internally.
